GotoScript
==========

Compiles Go into JavaScript excepting some Go's features which can not be
supported by JavaScript, like goroutines, channels, etc.

Status:

	const	[OK]
	itoa	[OK]


## Installation

	goinstall << DOWNLOAD URL >>
